<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2>
	Introduction</h2>
<p>This is a listing of 104 sites that legally offer free ebooks on Biographies, Autobiographies &amp; Memoirs, for reading.</p>
<p>There is a separate listing of sites offering free audiobooks in these genres:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong><a href="free-audiobooks-biography" target="_blank">Free Biography Autobiography and Memoir Audiobooks Online</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>All of these sites listed have content that is legal for them to distribute.  If you find that any site listed is offering content that can not be legally transferred, please let me know in the comments below. </p>
<p>This list is not comprehensive and if you know of any other sites please post in the comments below or at our <a href="freeware-forum/index.html" target="_blank">forums</a>. </p>
<p>A comprehensive alphabetical listing of free books for reading or listening can be found on these pages:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<a href="best-free-ebooks-online.htm" target="_blank"><strong>Best Free eBooks Online</strong></a>   (913 sites)</li>
	<li>
		<a href="free-books-audio" target="_blank"><strong>Best For Free Audio Books Online</strong></a>   (224 sites)</li>
</ul>
<p>For a complete listing of the free ebook pages here at Gizmo's, see</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong><a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/free-ebooks-and-audiobooks-to-read-online-or-download.htm" target="_blank">Free eBooks and Audio Books To Read Online Or Download</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>There will be other books on Biographies, Autobiographies &amp; Memoirs, at the sites listed there, but they are not categorized at the sites. </p>
<p>Libraries are also an excellent source for reading and listening materials.  To find out more information on your local library, the links here may help:  <a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/content/50-places-free-books-online.htm#libraries" target="_blank"><strong>Library Information</strong></a></p>
<h2>
	Biographies/Autobiographies/Memoirs Sites For Free eBooks</h2>
<p><a href="http://2020ok.com/2.htm" target="_blank"><strong>2020k (biographies &amp; Memoirs)</strong></a> Large collection of links to books divided into categories and sub-categories.  <strong>Note:</strong>  Most of the links here are working, but there are a number that lead to BookRags, which are not free anymore.  Unfortunately, there is no way of telling where the link goes until you click the link.  Since they did fix the issue with archive.org links, hopefully they will fix this. Thanks to Marie99 for pointing this out.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://digital.library.upenn.edu/women/wr-type.html#Biography" target="_blank">A Celebration of Woman Writers</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />a collection of links to free novels by woman writers.  Links are offsite, so download and viewing options vary. This link is to the Biography category.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.allahsword.com/free_islamic_books_biographies.html" target="_blank">Allah's Word</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />free Islamic books on Biographies.  All in English and available for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Best-Sellers-Kindle-Store-Biographies-Memoirs/zgbs/digital-text/154754011/ref=zg_bs_nav_kstore_3_157325011" target="_blank">Amazon</a></strong> has 100 of the top free ebooks in their Biographies &amp; Memoirs genre. If you click on the sub-genres on the left you will find many more free ebook offerings.   Using the tips provided at our page, <strong><a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/free-books-kindle" target="_blank">Places For Free Kindle eBooks Online</a></strong> you should be able to find even more free ebooks.  You do not need a Kindle to view these ebooks, there are free Kindle apps for every type of device and computer system.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://baptisthistoryhomepage.com/bapt.bios.html" target="_blank">Baptist History Homepage</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />has the biographies of over 600 prominent Baptist persons.  All are available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://bargainebookhunter.com/tag/biographies-memoirs/" target="_blank">Bargain eBook Hunter</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings in the Biographies &amp; Memoirs category.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.barnesandnoble.com/s/free-ebooks?dref=1%2C18933" target="_blank">Barnes &amp; Noble </a></strong>  has 7,914 free ebooks in its Biography genre available for free download in EPUB.  These are also broken down into several sub-genres.  Free registration is required.   This link is to the Books&gt;Biography genre.  There is also a link for <strong><a href="http://www.barnesandnoble.com/s/free-ebooks?dref=2207%2C3416" target="_blank">NOOK Books&gt;Biography &amp; Memoir</a></strong> which has the same number of free ebooks - not sure if they are all the same.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bibliomania.com/2/9/frameset.html" target="_blank"><strong>Bibliomania (Biographies)</strong></a> 8 biographies and autobiographies available for online viewing.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bibliotastic.com/genres/auto-biography" target="_blank">Bibliotastic</a></strong> has 6 free ebooks in their Auto Biography genre.  All are available for free reading online without registration.  All are available for free download in Kindle, EPUB and PDF, with free registration.  These are works of independent authors.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://blog.biographyfreebooks.com/" target="_blank">Biography Free Books</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offers in Biographies and Memoirs.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://bookgoodieskids.com/category/childrens-books/biographies/" target="_blank">Book Goodies For Kids</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free children ebooks offerings.   There is a nice category selection with a couple of free ebooks per category.  This link is to Biographies.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookiejar.com/home/browse?cat=18612224&amp;price=3&amp;status=2&amp;c=release&amp;type=Books" target="_blank">Bookie Jar</a></strong> has almost 2,616 free ebooks in its History, Biography &amp; Memoir  eBooks Free Classics category and 4 free ebooks in its <strong><a href="http://www.bookiejar.com/home/browse?cat=19136512&amp;price=0&amp;status=2&amp;c=release&amp;type=Books" target="_blank">History, Bio &amp; Memoir eBooks Free Indie</a></strong> category.  All are available for free reading online without registration.  Registration also allows free download in EPUB (Nook, iPad etc.) or Kindle compatible MOBI.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookrix.com/library.html?filterby=1&amp;category=5&amp;user=&amp;show=overview&amp;searchlang=en" target="_blank">BookRix </a></strong>370 free books in the autobiography &amp; biography category.  These are unique works by generally unpublished authors.  Available for free download, some as PDF, some as EPUB.  Be sure to click on the "Free Books" tab.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.booksie.com/memoir" target="_blank">Booksie</a></strong> has over 5,000 free entries in its Memoir category.  These include short stories, poetry and novels (by chapters).  All are original works of unpublished authors.  All are available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.booksinmyphone.com/?tag=bio" target="_blank">Books In My Phone</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />has 20 free ebooks in their Biography category.  These are MIDP for use on the phone.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.booksshouldbefree.com/genre/Biography" target="_blank"><strong>BooksShould Be Free</strong></a> is primarily an audio book download location, but it also has links to text versions of the works it has listed.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bookyards.com/categories.html?type=books&amp;category_id=4" target="_blank"><strong>BookYards (Biography/Memoirs)</strong></a> Over 700 works available for download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://drmfree.calibre-ebook.com/by/genre/biography?by=price" target="_blank">Calibre Open Books</a></strong> has 5 free ebooks in its Biography category.  Download and viewing options vary as these are links offsite.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.wmcarey.edu/carey/bios/biographies.htm" target="_blank">Carey Center</a></strong> <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />the Center for Study of the Life and Work of William Carey, D.D., has biographies of Dr. Carey and other influential Baptists.  Most are available for free reading online without registration.  There are some available for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://centslessbooks.com/biographies-and-memoirs.html" target="_blank">Centsless Books</a></strong> monitors Amazon (USA) for the top 100 free ebooks in the Biography &amp; Memoirs genre.  Updated hourly.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.classicly.com/autos-bios/books" target="_blank"><strong>Classicly </strong></a>has over 300 free ebooks in the autos &amp; bios section.  These are classic works in the public domain.  All are available for free download in PDF and many are also available in KINDLE.  Thanks to Tyler G for this suggestion.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.dailyfreebooks.co.uk/free_ebooks/latest/?source=both&amp;catID=58" target="_blank">Daily Free Books (UK)</a></strong>  monitors Amazon (UK) for its daily free offerings.  They offer genre selection as well as sorting by time (including since your last visit).  They also offer free listings from Smashwords, which can be viewed with the Amazon offerings, alone or not at all (Amazon only).  They have over 6,000 free ebooks listed.  This link is to the Biography &amp; Memoir genre listings for Amazon and Smashwords.  There were 66 free ebooks listed at the time of this post.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.dailyfreebooks.com/free_ebooks/latest/?source=both&amp;catID=58" target="_blank">Daily Free Books (USA)</a></strong>  monitors Amazon (USA) for its daily free offerings.  They offer genre selection as well as sorting by time (including since your last visit).  They also offer free listings from Smashwords, which can be viewed with the Amazon offerings, alone or not at all (Amazon only).  They have over 6,000 free ebooks listed.   This link is to the Biographies &amp; Memoirs genre listings for Amazon and Smashwords.  There were 51 free ebooks listed at the time of this post.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.dailylit.com/tags/biography/popular/1" target="_blank"><strong>DailyLit </strong></a> offers 40 free ebooks in its Biography category.  These are delivered in daily installments and some of the books are ongoing as of now.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.digilibraries.com/category/5/Biography__Autobiography/" target="_blank">DigiLibraries</a></strong> 840 free books in their biography &amp; autobiography category.  Most are available for free reading online as well as free download in PDF, MOBI and EPUB.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.digitalbookindex.org/_SEARCH/search010biogt.asp" target="_blank">Digital Book Index</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />provides links to free books around the web.  This link is to their collection of links under Biographies, Autobiographies, Memoirs.  There are additional selections under <strong><a href="http://www.digitalbookindex.org/_SEARCH/search010autobht.asp" target="_blank">Autobiographies, Biography</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.digitalbookindex.org/_search/search010hstuspresidentalbiogsa.asp" target="_blank">US History: Presidents Biographies</a></strong>.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebookdb.org/categories/Biographies-Novels-Memoirs/" target="_blank">eBook DB</a></strong> has over 200 free books in its biographies, novels &amp; memoirs, category.  These are links offsite, so download and viewing options vary.  From my quick look at the listings, not all are biographies, but still a good collection for this genre.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.ebooklobby.com/3/Biographies-&amp;-Memoirs" target="_blank"><strong>eBook Lobby (Biography &amp; Memoirs)</strong></a> 76 books available, some for online viewing some for PDF download.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.e-booksdirectory.com/listing.php?category=146" target="_blank">eBooks Directory</a></strong> has 54 free books in its biographies &amp; memoirs section.  These are links offsite, so download and viewing options vary.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooks-for-all.com/bookmarks/list/onecat/Free-ebooks+Letters-and-memoirs/0.html" target="_blank">eBooks For All </a></strong>has 4 free classic books in its letters &amp; memoirs section.  Links are offsite, so download and viewing options vary.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooksfree.com/category/memoir-biography" target="_blank">eBooks Free.Com </a></strong>has 3 free books in its memoir &amp; biography section available for free download in PDF (the books listed under "sponsors" are to be paid for)</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooksfreefreefree.com/free-at-amazon/nonfiction/biographies-and-memoirs/" target="_blank">eBooks Free Free Free</a></strong> monitors Amazon (USA) for the top free ebooks offerings in the Biographies ? Memoirs genre.  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />they also monitor the free iTunes ebooks:  <strong><a href="http://www.ebooksfreefreefree.com/itunes/nonfiction/biographies-memoirs/">iTunes: Biographies &amp; Memoirs</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooks-free-net.net/ebooks-free-biography.asp" target="_blank">eBooks FreeNet </a></strong>has 10 free books in its biography section available for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooksinternational.com/classics%20biography/classicsbiography.html" target="_blank">eBooks International </a></strong>has 13 free classics in its biography section available for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://ebooks-junkie.com/free-ebooks/biographies-and-memoirs/" target="_blank">eBooks-Junkie</a></strong>   has 45 free ebooks in its Biography &amp; Memoir genre listings.  These are gathered from sites around the web, so download and viewing options vary.  A mix of classic and new.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooksoneverything.com/biography.html" target="_blank">eBooks On Everything</a></strong> has 10 free classic biographies available for free download in PDF without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ebooktakeaway.com/non_fiction_autobiography_biography" target="_blank">eBookTakeaway </a></strong>has 80 free ebooks in its Autobiography &amp; biography section available for free download (zipped) in HTML, PDF &amp; EPUB.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://efreebooks.org/" target="_blank">eFree Books</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon for limited time free ebook offerings.  They do list genres, including Biography, but you have to select the genre for the day listed as there is not direct link to Biography listings.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.epubbooks.com/books/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=&amp;genre=Biography+%26+Autobiography&amp;author=&amp;sort_by=best_price&amp;sort_order=desc&amp;per_page=20" target="_blank"><strong>ePub Books</strong></a> has 4 free classic novels available in its biography/memoir section.  All are available for download in ePUB.  There are links to other download formats, but some of those are pay sites.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ereaderiq.com/freebies?c=154754011" target="_blank">eReader IQ</a></strong>   due to the changes in Amazon policy, they now offer an "abbreviated" listing of the limited time free book offers from Amazon .   They have a nice selection of genres to narrow the listings.  This link is to the <em>Biographies &amp; Memoirs</em> genre listings with Adult content blocked (you may click on the button on the upper right of the results to show Adult works).  There was 1 free ebook listed for this genre at the time of this post.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://ereaderlove.com/category/nonfiction/biographies-and-memoirs/" target="_blank">eReader Love</a></strong>    monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings.  This link is to their  Biographies &amp; Memoirs genre listings and at the time of this post, there were 23 free ebooks listed.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.ereaderperks.com/category/free-biography-memoir-nonfiction-books-for-nook-kindle-kobo/" target="_blank">eReaderPerks</a></strong>   monitors free releases at Amazon (as well as for Nook and Kobo) and has very good category listings.  This link is to their Biography genre free ebook offerings.  Offers email updates.  Thanks to <em>Lorie</em> for this listing.  Subscribers can now get customizable, genre-specific emails with the very latest freebie offers and the second addition is a daily list of the top 43-45 free book finds in all genres posted every morning on the homepage for a quick grab at the newest top-rated gems. (For Kindle, Kobo &amp; Nook).</p>
<p><strong>FeedBooks </strong>has 25 free books in its <a href="http://www.feedbooks.com/books/top?category=FBBIO000000&amp;range=week" target="_blank"><strong>PublicDomain(Biography &amp; Autobiography)</strong></a> section and 10 free books in its <a href="http://www.feedbooks.com/userbooks/top?category=FBBIO000000&amp;range=week" target="_blank"><strong>OriginalWorks(Biography&amp; Autobiography)</strong></a> section available for download in epub.</p>
<p><u><strong>Figment</strong></u> has almost 2000 free writings in its <strong><a href="http://figment.com/books/genre/Biography" target="_blank">Biography</a></strong> category and almost 5,000 free writings in its <strong><a href="http://figment.com/books/genre/Memoir" target="_blank">Memoir</a></strong> category.  These vary from short stories to full novels.  These are unique unpublished works.  All are available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.foboko.com/ebooks/biography-and-autobiographies" target="_blank">Foboko</a></strong>  has around 30 free novels available for free reading online or free download in TXT, PDF, EPUB, MOBIPocket and direct send to Kindle.  Free registration is required (I have received no spam) and there is a limit of 5 downloads per month (no limit on reading online).  There are some unique entries here.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://freediscountedbooks.com/category/free-books/perma-free/" target="_blank">Free &amp; Discounted Books </a></strong> <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />post links to free ebook offerings at Amazon (USA) This link is to their free biography ebook listings.  They also have <strong><a href="http://freediscountedbooks.com/category/free-books/autobiography/" target="_blank">Autobiography </a></strong>and <strong><a href="http://freediscountedbooks.com/category/free-books/memoirs/" target="_blank">Memoirs</a></strong>.</p>
