<p><strong><a href="http://www.freebooks.com/ebooks/?sort=title&amp;order=desc&amp;cat=biography" target="_blank">Free Books.com</a></strong> has two free novels in its biography section (Darwin and Lincoln) available fore free download in TXT, PDF, MOBI (Kindle) and EPUB.</p>
