<p><strong><a href="http://www.envisionthepast.com/" target="_blank">History of the Great Lakes States</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />this site has links to free online books and other materials relating to the USA states around the Great Lakes region.  This link is to the main page, which has a link to the Biographies and Memoirs for individuals from the region or specific states.</p>
