<p><strong><a href="http://www.librophile.com/#%21/ebooks/popular/free" target="_blank">Librophile</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />known mostly as an audiobook site, they also have links to free downloads of classic novels.   All of the links I looked at were to Project Gutenberg, which means they are available for free download in several formats as well as free reading online without registration.  You will need to select Biography under Genres as they do not allow direct links to the genre pages.</p>
