<p><strong><a href="http://www.nobooko.com/free-ebooks/?&amp;catID=10" target="_blank">Nobooko</a></strong>   has over 186 free ebooks in its Biography &amp; Memoir genre listing.  Most link to Kobo and are available for free download in EPUB after free registration (no credit card needed) at Kobo.  Since Kobo does not offer genre listings for its free ebooks, this is an excellent resource.  There are some Smashwords links in the results also.</p>
