<p><strong><a href="http://www.pdftitles.com/subject/biography" target="_blank">PDF Titles</a></strong>   has over 600 free classic ebooks in its Biography genre listings.  Despite the name of the site, these ebooks are all available for free download in a wide variety of formats, including PDF, EPUB and Kindle compatible formats.   There is a large selection of sub-genre.   A very nice collection with some unique entries.</p>
<p><a href="http://gutenberg.net.au/biography.html" target="_blank"><strong>Project Gutenberg Australia </strong></a>has a very nice listing of autobiographies available for download in a large number of formats.  Many of these link back to Gutenberg (above), but are listed in alphabetical order of the subject of the biography as opposed to the author.  Some of the entries are not available at Gutenberg.</p>
