<p><strong><a href="http://snickslist.com/books/browse-categories/9/Biographies--Memoirs/" target="_blank">Snick's List</a></strong>   monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings and has the nice feature of separate genre listings for these free ebooks.  This link is to the Biographies &amp; Memoirs genre free offerings.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.andrewfullercenter.org/blog/2013/02/free-andrew-fuller-biographies-available-online/" target="_blank">The Andrew Fuller Center</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />has links to biographies of the influential Baptist.  All the links I looked at were in Google Books and were available for free reading online without registration.</p>
