<p><a href="http://www.web-books.com/Category.php?Category=Biography" target="_blank"><strong>WebBooks</strong></a> has 66 free classic novels available in its biography category.  These are all available to read free online or for download in WEB and WEB database.  Viewing the downloads requires their <a href="http://www.web-books.com/Web/iDownload.htm" target="_blank">Web Viewer </a>(free) which is clean as far as I can tell</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.whsmith.co.uk/dept/ebooks-biography-true-stories-63550/list?_=1375953835789&amp;filters=FILTER_maxPrice_PWS_GB_GBP:%5B0.0+TO+0.0%5D&amp;page=1&amp;results=60&amp;sort=asc_bestSellerRanking" target="_blank">WHSmith</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />a UK site that teams with Kobo to offer ebooks.  This link is to their collection of free ebooks in their Biography and True Story collection.  All are available for free download in EPUB after registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Portal:Biography" target="_blank">WikiSource</a></strong> has a good size collection in its biography genre available for free reading online.  These all appear to be from the late 19th century and early 20th century.  Similar works are listed in the <strong><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Portal:Autobiographies" target="_blank">Autobiography</a></strong> section.</p>
